values.label: Calculation net
values.comment: The price stated is the net price including allowances/ charges. Allowances/charges may be stated for information only.

values.label: Calculation gross
values.comment: The price stated is the gross price to which allowances/ charges must be applied.

values.label: Allowances and charges not included, tax included
values.comment: The price does not include the allowances and charges, but includes the taxes.

values.label: Average selling price
values.comment: Average selling price of a product.

values.label: Information price, excluding allowances or charges, including taxes
values.comment: The price stated is for information purposes only and excludes all allowances and charges. Taxes however are included in the price.

values.label: Information price, excluding allowances or charges, and taxes
values.comment: The price stated is for information purposes only and excludes all allowances, charges and taxes.

values.label: Additive unit price component
values.comment: A code to indicate that the price described is an additive component of the total price.

values.label: Average purchase price
values.comment: Average purchase price of a product.

values.label: Calculation price
values.comment: The price stated is the price for the calculation of the line item amount.

values.label: Information
values.comment: The price is provided for information.

values.label: Invoice price
values.comment: Referenced price taken from an invoice.

values.label: Mutually defined
values.comment: A code assigned within a code list to be used on an interim basis and as defined among trading partners until a precise code can be assigned to the code list.
